Here are some repositories on GitHub related to movies:

1. [Khanhtran47 / Sora](^2^): A web app for exploring, watching movies, TV shows, and anime built with Remix and NextUI².
2. [QAZIMAAZARSHAD / Movie-Streaming-Website](^2^): A website to watch movies, anime, web series, and TV shows².
3. [codewithsadee / filmlane](^2^): Filmlane is a fully responsive movie website page².
4. [tushar-2223 / BlueBird-Movies](^2^): BlueBird-Movies is a React-based movie website that allows users to search for movies by title, sort them by genre, view trending and upcoming movies, and bookmark their favorite movies².
5. [codewithsadee / cineflix](^2^): Cineflix is another fully responsive movie website page².

Please note that these repositories are not necessarily related to the top 5 films, but they provide platforms for exploring, watching, and discussing various movies. You can check them out for more details..

